{
  "stem": "25114.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "One group was caught.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- and they were shot on the spot and left lying there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So the next day, everybody can see them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they-- they confiscated their ration of bread for the-- for a week.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was 200 when we were actually living in the ghetto, and this was the-- the separated the work of-- of the workshops.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the living quarters, was in the one.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "This-- this was established as a-- as a self-contained ghetto-- the tradespeople .",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that one was still there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Some-- some people were still in the other ghetto left-- the one that worked in the military barracks, and a few who had managed to survive.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They were there, in the other ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the rest, and they-- and they brought in some-- also some more from the villages and-- and small townships to fill it up.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And because I looked for that-- them-- the smaller ones.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I brought them here so it would be easier to get them together.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we saw that people escaped from-- the other ghetto's people start escaping through the-- because the other people were going out to work.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So they'd work this one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So they made contacts while on their way to work or sometime-- sometimes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "If they were caught, they were shot on the spot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It doesn't matter, because they tried.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But in this ghetto-- and it was-- by then it was called the [NON-ENGLISH], Nowogrodek-- [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It means a works camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], they called it in German.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we saw those people from [NON-ENGLISH] trying to escape.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And some of them succeeded.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "As I said, there was a whole lot of people there in the Pushcha.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But it wasn't our side.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "It was the other side of the Pushcha.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
